Get KenPom's conference comparison stats

Source: R/kp_historical_tables.R
kp_confstats.Rd

Get KenPom's conference comparison stats

Usage

kp_confstats(year = most_recent_mbb_season())

Arguments

year

Year (YYYY)

Value

A data frame with 35 columns:

  • Confcharacter.

  • Effdouble.

  • Eff.Rkdouble.

  • Tempodouble.

  • Tempo.Rkdouble.

  • eFG.Pctdouble.

  • eFG.Pct.Rkdouble.

  • TO.Pctdouble.

  • TO.Pct.Rkdouble.

  • OR.Pctdouble.

  • OR.Pct.Rkdouble.

  • FTRatedouble.

  • FTRate.Rkdouble.

  • Blk.Pctdouble.

  • Blk.Pct.Rkdouble.

  • Stl.Pctdouble.

  • Stl.Pct.Rkdouble.

  • FG_2.Pctdouble.

  • FG_2.Pct.Rkdouble.

  • FG_3.Pctdouble.

  • FG_3.Pct.Rkdouble.

  • FT.Pctdouble.

  • FT.Pct.Rkdouble.

  • FG_3A.Pctdouble.

  • FG_3A.Pct.Rkdouble.

  • A.Pctdouble.

  • A.Pct.Rkdouble.

  • HomeWLcharacter.

  • HomeWL.Pctdouble.

  • HomeWL.Rkdouble.

  • Closedouble.

  • Close.Rkdouble.

  • Blowoutsdouble.

  • Blowouts.Rkdouble.

  • Yearcharacter.

  try(kp_confstats(year=most_recent_mbb_season()))
